Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.statistics

Class StatisticsDto

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.statistics.StatisticsDto
public class StatisticsDto extends Object
Represents statistical data for the system. This class encapsulates various statistics, including total users, average users per project, average execution time per project, and lists of suppliers, members per lab, projects per lab, and projects status numbers per lab.
